{"tid":2297744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪人到中年就可以溝到女","createTime":"2020-11-23T13:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T13:06:29.000Z","uid":134500,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"da9f0481f305370f34dafaf7990fc486340570c0","tid":2297744,"uid":134500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"就變中佬有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日聽啲女講咩大叔控 <br />\n個個見到韓國個班孔劉呀玄彬呀個啲就濕撚晒<br />\n<br />\n啲港女可唔可以尊重下個一班<br />\n密密地變成中佬嘅香港代表<br />\n明明本地都有好多型棍中佬可以比你J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如林德信呀又識玩音樂又係星二代呢啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KN4pVZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKN4pVZd.png&h=8f1321ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZ04VZe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZ04VZe.png&h=67368f41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJB7TLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJB7TLV.jpg&h=810418f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有成日同孔劉撞樣嘅張松枝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6VTPju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6VTPju.jpg&h=0a8a97d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chsnHFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchsnHFb.jpg&h=12af633c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲後生小鮮肉個陣完全紅唔起<br />\n捱到中年先開始有人留意到<br />\n一個識玩音樂一個又有演技<br />\n希望真係在明天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他香港有才華嘅中佬型棍代表？"},{"pid":"d723ed1b3042c64103fa2e3df5496641d67c8783","tid":2297744,"uid":181319,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"人哋紅唔起，但唔係冇樣冇身材冇高度，所以老左都型姐，後生冇樣冇身材冇高度嘅話老左咪又係溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461b599a93f39ee64f72bd3a096b5514f585f1f1","tid":2297744